            <div class = "hero">
                <h2>Future Development Roadmap</h2>
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li style = "color: #6935B3"><strong>Expanded Data Integration:</strong> Incorporate more datasets covering a wider range of diseases, including both adult and pediatric conditions, to improve inclusivity metrics.</li>
                <li style = "color: #6935B3"><strong>Disease Library Expansion:</strong> Add new conditions and other studies to the database, ensuring a broader view of gender and age-related research gaps.</li>
                <li style = "color: #6935B3"><strong>Advanced Symptom Analysis:</strong> Develop tools to analyze a wider array of symptoms across populations to better detect underreported patterns, particularly in women and minorities.</li>
                <li style = "color: #6935B3"><strong>Comprehensive Diagnostic Support:</strong> Expand the Diagnostic Tool so that when professionals enter more detailed and complex patient symptoms, it could automatically generate tailored follow-up diagnostic questions for multiple conditions beyond Endometriosis.</li>
                <li style = "color: #6935B3"><strong>Predictive Bias Alerts:</strong> Implement an alert system that flags potential biases in new studies or clinical trials before publication, ensuring research inclusivity from the start.</li>
                <li style = "color: #6935B3"><strong>Policy & Advocacy Integration:</strong> Use the enhanced data and diagnostic insights to support advocacy for equitable healthcare research policies.</li>
            </ul>
